==FA Cup==
Gillingham entered the [[FA Cup]] at the fourth qualifying round, defeating fellow [[Kent]] club [[Maidstone United F.C.|Maidstone United]], then went on to beat another [[Non-league football|non-league]] club, [[Dulwich Hamlet F.C.|Dulwich Hamlet]].  The club was then eliminated by fellow Division Three team [[Northampton Town F.C.|Northampton Town]] in the sixth qualifying round.

