==Squad statistics==
[[Image:TommyHall1920.jpg|thumb|right|upright|Tommy Hall was the leading goalscorer for the season]]
Gillingham used a total of 26 players over the course of the season.  No player was ever-present, but captain [[Jock Robertson]], goalkeeper [[Jack Branfield]] and top goalscorer [[Tommy Hall (footballer)|Tommy Hall]] each missed only one match.
